{"tid":1690951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想唔想知點樣突破瓶頸位 就係你哋最唔想提嘅方法","createTime":"2019-11-03T12:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T13:13:50.000Z","uid":311193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"382b0870f2291599d95b48f5af3eaa8a53ac0b2b","tid":1690951,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武抗爭</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>嘅唯一出路</span></strong><br />\n我哋係要令人哋跪低 係要令人哋驚我哋呀<br />\n誰大誰惡誰正確呀 你知呢個世界係咁玩架 但你仲呃自己以為仲有其他方法令強權跪低？ 你聽到有狗呢兩隻字就跑到幾條街<br />\n和勇合一 但和理 你都要迫自己一日比一日行得更前先得<br />\n香港人 反抗唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">口號</span></span>嚟 係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span></span></strong>嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bxvu6r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bxvu6r.png&h=7ab599b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQUxJrt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQUxJrt.png&h=ea8c1b15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勇武會休息 直到贏咗呢場仗之後 一定休息<br />\n依家嘅你唔認同全民勇武 但之後一定會係勇武抗爭<br />\n我保證 之後一定會係全勇武抗爭 只差你迫唔迫自己一日比一日更勇敢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c34f1c95b1274676a803f00966d73a95478477","tid":1690951,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:58:06.000Z","msg":"推 前線手足一日比一日少"},{"pid":"1dfd93d3b5df039f070e8e0da8e6c64cb9db56ef","tid":1690951,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"推 全民勇武唔係只係口號"},{"pid":"3eba75572dd0b90dea395b25a89e70a8fad5158c","tid":1690951,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"唔好卻步好冇 大家嘅行動升級去咗邊"},{"pid":"5bfc6c199b85e05059fc0c53ba29fb0ff62ca170","tid":1690951,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB